{"tid":2351293,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息：今（3/1）增約40宗確診，強制檢測增至46廈","createTime":"2021-01-03T06:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T06:33:53.000Z","uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"71bd67d52b091a353f1515810b2a19aae54c0026","tid":2351293,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210103/422399946088517632805612.jpeg/TOxah-w6BVhOhRyfneNbBthTzdTw4G7EpHm5OKR5uTg?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210103%2F422399946088517632805612.jpeg%2FTOxah-w6BVhOhRyfneNbBthTzdTw4G7EpHm5OKR5uTg%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=95db235f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港新冠肺炎疫情持續。衞生署昨（2日）公布新增35宗確診個案，是近一個半月以來新低，累計增至8,924宗。消息指今日（3日）增約40宗確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n須強制檢測大廈新增3幢，包括深水埗福華街華寶樓、元朗水邊圍邨泉水樓，以及日出康城領凱第9座左翼，總數增至46幢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/569285/新冠肺炎-最新-消息-今增約40宗確診-強制檢測增至46廈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F569285%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E4%BB%8A%E5%A2%9E%E7%B4%8440%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B346%E5%BB%88&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0KnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=748e1c6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/569285/新冠肺炎-最新-消息-今增約40宗確診-強制檢測增至46廈</a>"},{"pid":"3c2011d17b00db8a41821911f868b0ed9f769ded","tid":2351293,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:09:45.000Z","msg":"回落了"},{"pid":"67c370fbd927f7ef1504442b6e46d48315e7d509","tid":2351293,"uid":198539,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:10:35.000Z","msg":"gym<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29bcd0cc22f0e6ec7ee26b853cae39c57933df92","tid":2351293,"uid":52459,"like":4,"disli